DataElement.preferredName: Left Ventricular Ejection Time Measurement Millisecond Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Numeric value to represent the time of ejection of blood from the left ventricle beginning with the opening of the aortic value and ending with aortic value closure, expressed as a number of milliseconds.
